View Project

Project Header

 

Project header contains the following information:

  1. Type - the type Project
  2. State - current Project state
  3. Name of the Project

Project Dashboard Tab

 

Once the Project is opened, the Project dashboard is displayed. In the Project dashboard you can find following information:

  1. Project Details - present the project details
  2. Cultural Objects  - the list with all cultural objects related to that Project
  3. Ongoing Activities  - displays activities like Projects, Conservation Activities and Tasks related to the Project that are in status In Progress
  4. Documents and media - displays documents and media related to the Project
  5. Related persons - the list with all assigned persons to the Project like Participant(s), Watchers, etc.
  6. Comments - latest comments on the project and the content created/uploaded in it

To access more detailed information select from following tabs:

  1. Details - to check the Project metadata
  2. Cultural Objects - to check the full list with all Cultural Objects related to that Project
  3. Documents - to check the full list with all documents related to the Project
  4. Media - to check the full list with all images related to the Project
  5. Activities - to check the full list with all Activities to the Project
  6. System Data - to check system data related to the Project
  7. Permissions - to check the applied permissions on the Project
  8. Versions - to check the versions on the Project
